76561198140254664,Recommended,322850,17430047,"Posted: 7 August, 2015",all,Batang_Batibot,"Well, what else can I say. I love cycling so much that I don't care about the negative reviews. So far Cyanide is the best producer of Cycling simulator game in the market today. There are certainly some bugs and lot of improvements to be done, but I still enjoyed this game as much as I've enjoyed the previous versions.It's so rewarding to see your Pro cyclist in a pro mode beating the likes of Froome, Contador, etc. In the mountains and be able to replicate Jens Voigt's ""Shut up legs and do as I say"".I will certainly recommend this game to those die hard cycling lovers. I honestly say that this game is quite improving and I hope someday they will hit the mark where we fans will said ""well done Cyanide"", still hoping for that version to come.I suggest that you visit the community sites likePCMdaily.comfor some realistic databases. So I will give this game a rating of 8/10, for bringing up some new contents."
